  "text": "Our method's goal is to achieve as close an allocation as possible to that in Avissar et al. [CITATION_1] . In particular, we will emulate the run-time behavior of [CITATION_2] to the extent possible including its use of a distributed stack. However, our mechanisms at compile-time and loading-time will be significantly different from their method, and more complicated, because of the difficulties introduced by not knowing the SPM's size at compile-time.",
